   So if no one else has asked then good, that puts me at top of the list. Khoal, any chance of you putting a raid together? This comming weekend may be too early and the next weekend is President's weekend so some people may have plans. How about the weekend of the 24th? That should be enough time for people to commit to. If nothing else I would just the opportunity to group with fellow guild members. <br>
<br>
